AI => Inson aqliga taqlid qiladigan dastur.

AI => 
  - Machine Learnig (ML) => 
      - Supervised Machine Learning (SML) =>
          - Classification =>
              - Binary (targetimiz 2 turli qiymatga ega bolishi kera)
              - multi-class (targetimiz 3 va undan ortiq qiymatga ega bolishi kerak)
          - Regression (target qiymatimiz cheksiz bolishi kerak)
      - Unsupervised Machine Learning (USML)
      - Reinforcement Machine Learning (RML)


Ml model structure:
1. Data collection (raw data)
2. Data preprocessing (handling missing values, encoding categorical data, scaling/normalization)
3. Model (ALgorithm) selection
4. Model training (fitting the model)
5. Prediction (model output qaytaradi yangi datalarni kirgizganimizda )
6. Evaluation (modelimiz qay darajada yaxshi ishladi yoki yoq. accuracy score past chiqsa Model improvement bosqichini ham amalga oshirish kerak)
7. Testing (Bevosita natija olish)
8. Deployment



Data preprocessing:

1. Handling missing values => MEAN(numerical), MODE(object and numerical), MEDIAN(numerical), DROP(row and col), FIXED

2. Encoding => Categorical qiymatlarni numerical ga o'tqazish. Ya'ni object data type dan integer yoki float ga o'tish.
- one-hot encoding (classlar sonicha ustun yaratadi)
- label encoding (qiymatlari alifbo tartibida numerical qiymatlarga o'zgartiriladi.)
- frequency encoding (Takrorlanishlar sonini umumiy elementlar soniga nisbati. )
- target encoding (mean) (mos target qiymatning o'rta arifmetigi. )
- ordinal encoding (Ketma ketlik ga qarab sonlar bilan almashtiriladi.)

3. Scaling => Juda katta va juda kichik qiymatlarni balanslashtirish.
=> Standart, MinMax va Robust
MinMax => 0 va 1 oraliqqa olib kelib beradi. qolgan ikkalasdida manfiy tomonga ham otib ketib qoladi.


Algorithm Selection:

ML ALgorithm larni 2ga bolamiz => linear and non-linear

Liner =>
1. Liner => Liner regression (Regression)
         Logistic regression (Classification)

Non-liner =>
1. Tree-based => Decision tree
              Random forest

2. Distance-based => KNN
                  SVM

3. Ensemble => Random forest
            Gradient boosting


Logistic regression: Classification tasklar uchun ishlaydi.
Logistic Regression bosqichlari=> 
  Data preprocessing (cleaning, encoding, scaling)
  x, y (inputs(features) va outpu(target) ni aniqlash)
  splitting (train va test)
  Trainig(fitting)
  Predicting
  Evaluating

Linear regression => input va output qiymatlar uchun mos chiziq topib berish
y=B0+B1x+e => linear equation 
x-input
y-output
B (Betta)-parametr
e (Epsilyon)-error (Hech qachon nol bolmaydi) e!=0

Linear regression 2 ga bolinadi => Simple va Multiple.



Library => Kodlar jamlanmasi. Qayta qayta kod yozmasligimiz uchun ishlatiladigan package.

- Numpy, 
- Pandas, 
- Matplotib, 
- Seaborn, 
- Scikit-learn => Eng katta kutubxonalardan biri.


Python:

- Data Types (Ma’lumot turlari): Bu o‘zgaruvchida saqlanadigan ma’lumot turini bildiradi.

int — butun sonlar
float — kasr sonlar
str — matnli ma’lumotlar
bool — mantiqiy qiymatlar (True / False)

- Operations (Amallar): Bu ma’lumotlar ustida bajariladigan amallar
Arithmetic: +, -, *, /
Comparison: ==, !=, >, <
Logical: and, or, not
Ular hisob-kitob, taqqoslash va mantiqiy tekshiruvlarda ishlatiladi.

- Conditions (Shart operatorlari): Dasturda qaror qabul qilish uchun ishlatiladi.
if
elif
else
Shartlar yordamida ma’lumot tekshiriladi va natijaga qarab turli kodlar bajariladi.

- For loop: Jarayonni avtomatlashtirish uchun ishlatilinadigan kodlar bloki.



